{"tid":384482,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[純發洩]Apple 啲嘢品質真係愈嚟愈差","createTime":"2017-09-02T10:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T11:03:12.000Z","uid":115189,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc20964eb9ba60f5925bf8598dab3991f6b3f5aa","tid":384482,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"當年部iPhone 4由老豆用到落我手3年都冇整過<br />\n<br />\n而家我手頭上啲Apple Products 全部都拎過曬去Genius bar 整咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n部iPhone 一買翻嚟就Speaker 冇聲，換過成部比我（仲要翻新機嚟）<br />\n<br />\n隻耳機得一邊有聲，又要換過隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家部MacBook Keyboard 冇反應，等咗幾日話我知整好，點知check 完仲係有問題，又要放低幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全部都保養期內出曬事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住年尾買隻AW奬勵下自己，而家真係不了，都唔知係奬勵定受罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c462f29b52e0c36ad2caaddf457e648e966be13c","tid":384482,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:40:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"981a834dabb647c18125cda951a6fbba9072bd45","tid":384482,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"用家問題"},{"pid":"99f7753ba93c647810b349946b00538f7a27385b","tid":384482,"uid":115189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ON9仔人地都唔預你去整<br />\n<br />\n一年換一代咪正常囉<br />\n<br />\n邊有人估到你唔肯換新 要維修呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未過保，一年都未過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9249a8b51a8565a9f64f625c860089073046fc89","tid":384482,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-